---
<BaseLayout
  title="Cash Home Sale Resources & Articles | Cash Guy Nate"
  description="Articles and resources on cash home sales in Arizona. The math, the process, the legal landscape, the honest tradeoffs."
  pageType="trust"
  crumbs={[{ label: "Home", href: "/" }, { label: "Articles" }]}
>
  <section class="container container--narrow">
    <h1>Articles & Resources</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.6;">
      Honest writing on how the cash-buyer market actually works in Arizona. No fluff, no sales pitches inside the articles — we save the pitch for the call.
    </p>
    <p>
      Most of what gets written about cash home buyers online is either thinly-veiled marketing or generic advice that doesn't account for Arizona's specific legal and market context. The articles below are different: real Arizona Revised Statute references, real Phoenix-metro and Tucson market data, real anonymized scenarios from deals we've actually closed, and honest tradeoffs about when cash buyers are the right call and when they aren't.
    </p>
    <p>A few articles to start with depending on your situation:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Deciding between cash and listing:</strong> Start with <a href="/blog/cash-offer-vs-listing-math/">Cash Offer vs. Listing: The Math</a> for a full breakdown of what each path actually nets you in 2026.</li>
      <li><strong>Comparing cash buyers:</strong> Read <a href="/blog/best-cash-home-buyers-phoenix/">9 Best Cash Home Buyers in Phoenix</a> for an honest review of every active operator in the Phoenix market, including us.</li>
      <li><strong>Behind on payments or pre-foreclosure:</strong> <a href="/blog/i-need-to-sell-my-house-fast/">I Need to Sell My House Fast</a> covers the realistic options under tight timelines.</li>
      <li><strong>Executor managing an estate:</strong> <a href="/blog/sell-house-during-probate-arizona/">Selling a House in Probate in Arizona</a> walks through A.R.S. Title 14 specifics.</li>
      <li><strong>Curious about the numbers:</strong> <a href="/blog/what-cash-buyers-actually-pay/">What Cash Buyers Actually Pay</a> breaks down the 65-80% of ARV math with neighborhood-specific factors.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      All articles are updated to reflect the 2026 market. Comments and corrections welcome — call (602) 555-0100.
    </p>
    <hr style="margin: 2.5rem 0 1.5rem; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e8e4dc;" />
    <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">All articles</h2>
    {posts.map((p) => (
      <article style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e3dd; padding: 1.4rem 0;">
        <h2 style="margin-top: 0;"><a href={`/blog/${p.slug}/`} style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-primary);">{p.title}</a></h2>
        <p style="color: #6a6a6a; font-size: 0.88rem; margin: 0 0 0.5em;">{new Date(p.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
        <p style="margin: 0;">{p.excerpt}</p>
      </article>
    ))}
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
